data.description: Our inviting, affordable brand-new Richmond plan creates a welcoming ambiance for family and guests. This designer home offers more than 1,900+ sq ft of charming living space complete with 4-bedrooms, 3-bathrooms, and a full 2-car garage. Other features include an open layout overlooking the kitchen, living and dining areas, a covered patio space, GE kitchen appliances, kitchen island, and cultured marble bathroom countertops, and a Bonus room located upstairs. The Richmond is outfitted with exterior craftsman style touches. Don’t wait to call it your new home, schedule an appointment today!
